You can find the development log here:
https://www.clublexus.com/forums/lc-model-2018-present/953935-building-a-remote-for-the-stock-exhaust.html

Install Dependencies in dependecies folder:

bcm2835:

cd bcm2835-1.60/
sudo ./configure
sudo make
sudo make check
sudo make install

wiringPi:

sudo apt-get install wiringpi
#When used on Raspberry Pi 4B, you may need to upgrade firstï¼š
sudo dpkg -i wiringpi-latest.deb
gpio -v
# Run the command "gpio -v". If the version 2.52 is displayed, the installation is successful
